he British ''[[Journal of Ecclesiastical History]]''.<ref>{{cite book|last=Bradley|first=James E.|title=Church History: An Introduction to Research, Reference Works, and Methods|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RpuVtoUQuy8C&pg=PA90|year=1995|publisher=Wm. B. Eerdmans|isbn=9780802808264|page=90}}</ref>
